Airbnb Analytics Dashboard Report

The Airbnb Analytics Dashboard is an interactive business intelligence solution developed in Power BI to analyze Airbnb listing data. The dashboard transforms raw data into meaningful visualizations, allowing users to explore pricing, host performance, customer ratings, room types, and neighbourhood-level trends.

This project focuses on converting large volumes of Airbnb data into actionable business insights through KPI cards, DAX calculations, interactive filters, and visual analytics.

Project Objectives
Understand Airbnb market performance.
Analyze listing distribution.
Compare neighbourhood performance.
Evaluate host contributions.
Study pricing behaviour.
Monitor review trends.
Build an interactive reporting solution.
